This is the Wordpress theme for inclusivedesign.ca, the website of the Inclusive Design Institute.


For video player within IDI site (IDI-104):

	Clone videoplayer into wp-content/themes/idi-theme/lib
	In wp admin area, create top-level page "Media" and assign template "Media" to it
	
	header.php: temporary, includes video player files and changes to UIO. Copy back to wp-fss-theme when VP is ready.
	media.php:	media page with video player content
	sidebar-media.php:	sidebar for media page
	/videos: 	video files for media page
